1. e4 c5 2. d4 cxd4 3. c3 a6?! 4. Nf3?! (4. cxd4! { Don't try to force the game back to theory. Stick to the general principles. }) 4... d6 (4... dxc3 5. Nxc3 d6 6. Bc4 Nc6 7. O-O Nf6) 5. cxd4 Bg4 6. h3 (6. Bc4!? { an interesting idea. } 6... Nc6? (6... Nf6 7. Bxf7+?? Kxf7 8. Ng5+ Ke8) 7. Bxf7+ Kxf7 8. Ng5+ Ke8 9. Qxg4) (6. Qb3!? b5 7. a4 bxa4 8. Rxa4) 6... Bxf3 7. Qxf3 Nf6 8. Nc3?! (8. e5! { Push knight, win space! } 8... dxe5 9. dxe5 (9. Qxb7) 9... Nd5 10. Bc4 (10. Bg5)) 8... e6 9. Bc4 b5 10. Bb3 (10. e5 Nbd7 11. exf6 bxc4 12. fxg7 Bxg7) 10... Nc6 11. Be3 Be7? 12. O-O? (12. e5! { Tactical weaknesses! }) 12... Qc7 13. d5! (13. Rac1! O-O 14. d5! exd5 15. Nxd5 Nxd5 (15... Qd7 16. Nb6! (16. Rxc6! Qxc6 (16... Nxd5 17. exd5) 17. Nxe7+)) 16. exd5 Ne5 17. Rxc7 Nxf3+ 18. gxf3) 13... Ne5 14. Qe2 exd5 15. Nxd5 Nxd5 16. Bxd5! (16. exd5) 16... Rd8 17. Rac1 Qd7 (17... Qb8) 18. f4! { Push knight, win space! More forcing than Bf4. } (18. Bf4? O-O 19. Bxe5 dxe5 20. Bc6) 18... Nc4 19. b3! (19. Bd4 O-O (19... f6) 20. b3 Na5 21. Qe1) 19... O-O (19... Nxe3 20. Bc6 Qxc6 21. Rxc6 Nxf1 22. Qxf1) 20. bxc4 bxc4 21. Bxc4 Rc8 22. Bxa6 Rxc1 23. Rxc1 d5 24. exd5 Qxd5 25. Rc8 Rxc8 26. Bxc8 g6 27. Ba6 Bh4 28. Bc4 Qb7 29. Bd4 Qd7 30. Qe5 { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0


